Crauford Kent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crauford_Kent 0 Crauford Kent (12 October 1881 – 14 May 1953) was an English-born character film actor, in the United States. He has also been credited as Craufurd Kent and Crawford Kent. Crauford_Kent ( 12_October_1881 – 14_May_1953 ) was an_English-born_character_film_actor , in the_United_States . He has_also_been_credited as Craufurd_Kent and Crawford_Kent .
